```python
def transform(sequence):
    transformed_sequence = [0]*len(sequence)
    nonzero_indices = [i for i, num in enumerate(sequence) if num != 0]
    zeros = [i for i in range(len(sequence)) if i not in nonzero_indices]
    for i in range(len(nonzero_indices)):
        transformed_sequence[zeros[i]] = sequence[nonzero_indices[i]]
    return transformed_sequence
```
